Low Level Data Quality Checks
[Data Quality, alcapana]

Low level data quality checks. More...

Modules

 MDQ_Amplitude
 

Histograms the TPI amplitudes for each detector. Creates a number of amplitude plots, where the amplitude is in units of ADC counts.


 MDQ_DAQLivetime
 

Stores fraction of run time that data was being taken. Creates hDQ_DAQLivetime.


 MDQ_DigitizerOverflow
 

Plots information related to FADC sample overflow, as in samples that went off scale.


 MDQ_FADCBufferOverflow
 

Plots information related to FADC buffer overflow, as in when the data buffer is full and no more data can be taken.


 MDQ_FADCPacketLoss
 

Plots information related to loss of FADC packets over the network.


 MDQ_IslandCounter
 

Plots number of TPIs in each detector per MIDAS event with different normalizations.


 MDQ_IslandLength
 

Plots information related to length of TPIs in each bank per MIDAS event.


 MDQ_IslandRate
 

Plots TPI rate in each bank per MIDAS event.


 MDQ_IslandTimestamp
 

Histograms the timestamps from each MIDAS event for each detector.


 MDQ_muScTDiff
 

Correlations of TPI timestamps with timestamps in muSc.


 MDQ_PulseShapes
 

Plots the persistance plots and Y projections of these, along with pedestal and pedestal noise of each bank averaged over the run.


 MDQ_RunTime
 

Records run time according to the ODB.


 MDQ_TDCCheck
 

Plots information from the TDC, most importantly muSc, muScA, and muPC data.


 MDQ_Thresholds
 

Record thresholds from the ODB.
